Star Surfer is a fast-paced arcade game inspired by Subway Surfers, set in a space universe.
The player controls an astronaut who must dodge meteorites, collect stars, and survive until the time runs out.

Simple mechanics, addictive gameplay, and constant challenge make Star Surfer a fun and dynamic experience.


